commit_message:
Make pluggable API extensions

Reasons:
 - One of the stages in refactoring for multi-datastores purposes.

Changes:
 - Providing abstract API extension class(interface);
 - making extension routes pluggable (per datastore manager);
 - fixing tests;

Change-Id: Ib3b24ab5b9bbd5bf42199071554df73e07624b6a
Implements: blueprint trove-refactoring-for-better-pluggability
